metadata.name: Dungeons: A Heroes NFT Collection
metadata.description:
Play your Hero in the Dungeons! Fight Rats, Skeletons, and the Hordes! Get Gold, Experience, and Loot! Beat Merlin's Challenge ...and later... Save the kingdom!

Dungeons are a set of 3,333 programatically generated dungeon maps based on the on-chain data from Crypts and Caverns to be played in the Heroes universe.
